text:
Ohio’s standard of living has been sinking for eight straight years under Republican rule. Not slipping — crashing. Higher costs, lower wages, crumbling infrastructure, families barely keeping their heads above water.
Now you can feel it: Ohioans are fed up. Done With GOP 
